{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c29af4094f","title":"《麻城县万人大会大会简报》第16期","origin":"湖北省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b61b2300af","index":0,"year":1959,"month":3,"day":30,"articleId":"c29af4094f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1d33483616","type":"title","text":"《麻城县万人大会大会简报》第16期","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"e65817fdf7","type":"paragraph","text":"[内部文件，后会收回]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"6e3a430c49","type":"subtitle","text":"中一公社","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"56c40a4d6d","type":"paragraph","text":"中一公社到会全体干部在查清收入、清理财务工作中，由于思想工作作得比较好，同志们自觉交待和揭发了别人的许多新问题，但是就整个情况来说，发展还是不够平衡的，有些人由于思想顾虑未解除，还不能推诚相见，概括起来有“四说四不说”的倾向。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"0b13f8a418","type":"paragraph","text":"一说57年的问题不说58年的问题。迎集大队十二个小社到会的40多个干部，光说57年生产好，收成好，对58年的生产不表示态度，彭畈三社干部承认57年贪污了13个棺材，58年是清清白白。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"9bc7de8075","type":"paragraph","text":"二说小问题不说大问题。迎集一社主任范志林说：去年腊月三十日，干部合伙贪污了50元，社干得5元，队干得3元，据了解有些重大问题都不交待。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"7763eb5035","type":"paragraph","text":"三说垮台干部不说在职干部。彭畈三社到会的二十多个干部，人人揭发前主任彭士清，贪污瞒产，对现有的干部一字不提。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"69a6e4fbca","type":"paragraph","text":"四说58年棉花跃进了，不说稻谷跃进了。王集三社五小队×光焕稻谷本来增了产，他说减了产，后来把帐对出来，稻谷照报社产量多2,400多斤，小麦2,333多斤。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"f99abdedf4","type":"paragraph","text":"公社党委针对思想情况，分头作了动员，采用个别串连、包干发动等办法，已收到显著效果，但还需进一步做好思想工作。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"4a6041d190","type":"paragraph","text":" 1959年3月30日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"a359559454","type":"subtitle","text":"龟山公社","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"074117c908","type":"paragraph","text":"八笔胡涂帐","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"d0b3b20514","type":"paragraph","text":"龟山人民公社原五星十一社，通过学习，提高了思想，暴露和揭发了不少问题。这个社的干部，在公社化后，贪污挪用，大吃大喝。据初步揭露有八笔胡涂帐：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"3d2221deb0","type":"paragraph","text":"第一笔：以中队长周兆吉为首的大吃大喝，欠供销部240元，由中队代付了。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"f6ada866f5","type":"paragraph","text":"第二笔：少报稻谷产量。原来报的稻谷总产270,339斤，实际产量为279,693斤，少报产量8,354斤。这批粮食也不知下落。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"0645774af6","type":"paragraph","text":"第三笔：少报花生产量。帐上只有11,834斤，各队统计为12,167斤，少报了333斤。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"f6952326ff","type":"paragraph","text":"第四笔：少报桐子产量。帐上只有1,000斤，各队综合为1,562斤，少报了562斤。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"baa0516624","type":"paragraph","text":"第五笔：茶子无帐可查，各队共卖了660斤，折人民币72.6元。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"6d2f238b41","type":"paragraph","text":"第六笔：十化投资，金银铜铁等物折人民币643元，既未上交，群众也未得分文。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"29c65f9ed7","type":"paragraph","text":"第七笔：卖木材80元，三个干部私分了，没有交待。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"545e1b8d7f","type":"paragraph","text":"第八笔：干部私分公款218元。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"bfe9f32baf","type":"paragraph","text":"以上八笔帐，计人民币1,869元，到会干部表示决心要搞清楚。他们还贴出了这样一张大字报：","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"66787ed158","type":"paragraph","text":"财经权力往下放，分配一定搞停当，这次我们查收入，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"b8f41493cb","type":"paragraph","text":"算出八笔狗肉帐，三个干部用五百，千元收入光溜光；","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"},{"id":"35ef136adf","type":"paragraph","text":"不怕他们鬼计多，定搞清楚才舒畅，定要算清胡涂帐。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f"}],"page":{"id":"f9ab15d140","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c29af4094f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}